                            <li>Usage Data: Information about how you interact with our service, including your IP address, browser type, operating system, and pages visited.</li>
                            <li>Cookies and Tracking Technologies: We may use cookies, web beacons, and other tracking technologies to collect information about your use of the service and to improve your experience.</li>
                        </ul>

